snippet.title: The Legend of Excalipurr Kickstarter/Greenlight announcement trailer
snippet.description:
The Legend of Excalipurr (formerly Attack On Kitten) is a 2D side-scrolling platform game, developed by Wisp Entertainment, a Louisiana-based independent video game developer.

Like us on Facebook: https://facebook.com/TheLegendofExcalipurr/

Official site: http://www.excalipurr.com/
